_aChangeLog.text: Map now has a working minimap on top left side.
Changed geometry on spawns so it's not as complex
All assets are neatly packed into a single .bsp file
Improved the H on helipads, now it's a model.
REMOVED THOSE GODAWFUL CT AND T SIGNS!!!

_sText:
This map is the 2nd in hopefully several other maps that will come after.

It is part of project- ''Wintermaze_2016'' that im working on. 

Player count; 20vs20

Now I know what you think...''It's a goddamn maze!!''. Think of it more like a maze like structure. A series of protective walls to prevent the player from getting sniped. My goal here is not to get the player lost in the maze! 

I hope that you will enjoy the gameplay and have fun! :)

And remember! 

When swimming in pipes always look up! 

Feel free to comment and by all means let me know if you find any bugs or other issues of the map.
